#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
#include <vector>
using namespace std;

int main()
{
    int t;
    cin >> t;
    while (t--) {
        int n;
        vector<int> v;
        cin >> n;
        int a;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            cin >> a;
            v.push_back(a);
        }
        sort(v.begin(),v.end());
        for (int i = 0; i < n-1; i++)
            cout << v[i] << " ";
        cout << v[n-1] << endl;
    }
    return 0;
}
